description: Roaming through Askian, the Bitrail Enchanter rumbles along with a shimmer of digital delight. At each stop, the townsfolk eagerly offer their Talismans, seeking a touch of crystal-enchantment. Beneath a connecting sign for Bitrails and Blocktrails the journey unfurls, leaving in its wake a tapestry woven with charm and whispers of magic.
name: BITRAILSCD
